      <p>A roommate of mine from school had a really rough go of it with postpartum depression after delivering her firstborn. I remember talking with her when she was completely in the thrall of it. And I can safely say, she has come out with flying colors and two other kids. So, I&#39;m glad you got the help and support you need, and there is another side. Hang in there Molly.</p>
