    <div class="comment--content">
      <p>Kudos to you for sharing.  I&#39;m not a mom myself, but I&#39;ve often wondered why everyone doesn&#39;t go through that &#8211; so much is changing and so much is new once you have a kid.  Take care of yourself and know that you don&#39;t have it do it all alone &#8211; don&#39;t be afraid to lean on others.  I bet putting a name to it must have been such a relief.  You&#39;ll get through it &#8211; just don&#39;t try to hurry it.  You only need to take on one day at a time.  Best wishes to you all.  </p>
    </div>

