      <p>Thank you for sharing. I did not have postpartum, but my mom did, and so have many of my friends. I did have a week of depression right before I gave birth, and it is scary and unsettling and I felt guilty for not being excited about my child. But it is important to get help, and I&#39;m so glad you did, for yourself and for June, and I&#39;m so glad you shared your story for all the other moms out there that have experienced this. For any mom out there fighting post partum, you are strong and brave and a wonderful mom because you are taking care of yourself. 🙂</p>
