      <p>Molly, I&#39;m so sorry to hear about your ppd.  But glad to hear you are getting treatment and feeling much better.  I know that depression is treatable since I have experienced it and been successfully treated.  Now depression is mostly in the past for me. Psychologists helped me and also a very good book called Happiness is a Choice by Minirth Meyer.  It is excellent for anyone who might experience depression and was truly a lifesaver to me.</p>
