    <div class="comment--content">
      <p>It is so normal. I had it with both of my children, but it was much worse with my second child. The kicker for me was that I has such a hard time conceiving that it seemed a cruel joke to be left feeling so depleted when all that I had longed for had finally come to fruition.</p>
<p>It is imperative to get and accept the help&#8230; and you will come out on the other side so much stronger than you can imagine. But&#8230;you will take many tiny steps, forward and back, until you find the right groove.</p>
<p>Thank you for sharing this.</p>
