    <header class="comment--meta">
      <div class="vcard"><cite class="comment-author fn"><a href="https://www.blogger.com/profile/14943701967122920362" class="url" rel="ugc external nofollow">Lizzytish</a></cite></div>
      <a href="https://orangette.net/2013/01/ah-ha/#comment-39881"><time class="comment-time" datetime="2013-01-08T22:41:46-05:00">Tuesday, January 8, 2013 at 10:41 pm</time></a>    </header>

    
    <div class="comment--content">
      <p>Molly,<br />First, your baby is gorgeous! Second, I have been suffering from panic and anxiety that I am pretty sure has been brought on by peri-menopause, and I know just how you&#39;re feeling! You can&#39;t reason yourself out of it, so seeking help is the way to go. I hope you feel better soon!</p>
