    <div class="comment--content">
      <p>Just one more voice telling you that you absolutely will get through it.  Take all the help that is offered.  Trust your doctors/family/misc support systems to help you to the other side.  Post-partum depression is terrible, and I wish we both had been spared, but you will get out the other side and be yourself again.  Just take it a day/hour/moment at a time. It will get better little by little until one day you will realize it&#39;s gone.</p>
