    <div class="comment--content">
      <p>Hi Molly, I found your site thru Sophie Dahl&#39;s list of favorite sites.  For the last two years between admiring your photographs and recipes, I have always found a sort of peaceful start to my morning.  Yours is one of a few that I check up on daily.  Reading your blog thru your pregnancy and now seeing June develop into such a beautiful child has been joyous.   This time will pass and you will get better.   You are so lucky to have been diagnosed and are getting the treatment.   I wasn&#39;t so lucky nineteen years ago so after all the news about postpartum depression I feel so happy you young mothers today are getting help.  Love to you and your beautiful family!  Michele</p>
