    <div class="comment--content">
      <p>What a beautiful, beautiful baby!</p>
<p>I too went through this and can assure that it does indeed pass.  It fees big, it feels like there is nothing outside of it, and (to me, at least) it feels somewhat unnatural &#8230; I mean, here I was with this perfect beautiful baby, and I just wanted to cry all the time, but it does pass.  Believe it or not, you will look back even on the hard hard newborn days and remember all the little pieces of joy and discovery with love and happiness.</p>
