    <div class="comment--content">
      <p>I&#39;ve never commented before, but I love your writing. I too had PPD but mine went undiagnosed for a long time &#8211; like a year. I can barely think about that time without cringing. Though you are probably not thinking about this now, I didn&#39;t want to have another baby for 5 years after my first because of my PPD. After my second, I had what I can only describe as postpartum euphoria, must to my surprise and joy. Hang in there. It is a tough row to hoe, but you can come out the other end with great joy.</p>
