    <header class="comment--meta">
      <div class="vcard"><cite class="comment-author fn">Anonymous</cite></div>
      <a href="https://orangette.net/2013/01/ah-ha/#comment-39517"><time class="comment-time" datetime="2013-01-12T15:35:46-05:00">Saturday, January 12, 2013 at 3:35 pm</time></a>    </header>

    
    <div class="comment--content">
      <p>My memories of pregnancy, childbirth, etc, are of suddenly not being myself. I don&#39;t think I was depressed&#8211;way too busy for any self examination, but it was a period of being overwhelmed by circumstances outside of my control. Allow yourself to be unhappy and out of control&#8211;you can come through it. Your life will not be perfect (I doubt it was before), but can be satisfying and fun again. Your beautiful baby will be his own person, so try very hard to sit back and watch him become what he wants to be. Your life&#39;s journey will be richer for him.</p>
    </div>

