    <div class="comment--content">
      <p>Dear Molly,<br />Any form of depression is scary. I&#39;ve battled with depression and have two friends who have and have had ppd. We all feel it&#39;s somehow our fault, that we should just try harder, see the brighter side but once you notice that it&#39;s hormones and an illness it will get better.<br />Mine sneaks up on me regularly and I help myself by exercising (seems to give me a boost) and accepting that it can happen and will pass.<br />Take care, big hugs</p>
