    <div class="comment--content">
      <p>Good for you for writing about this, life, including motherhood, isn&#39;t always what we think it will be.  Pregnant women are warned about lack of sleep and all that but no one warns you how completely overwhelming it all is, and how you might feel totally inadequate.  I can relate.  I wasn&#39;t diagnosed or anything, I may not have technically had PPD, but I DID feel totally overwhelmed, inadequate, and very tearful.  But it got better! Hang in there!</p>
    </div>

