      <a href="https://orangette.net/2013/01/ah-ha/#comment-39546"><time class="comment-time" datetime="2013-01-16T21:01:29-05:00">Wednesday, January 16, 2013 at 9:01 pm</time></a>    </header>

    
    <div class="comment--content">
      <p>I just found your lovely blog because I regularly check Postpartum Progress, which linked to you.  I work with women suffering (from what we like to gently, respectfully call) perinatal mood concerns.  I am a social worker.  And a mom.  And yes, more than anything, women who are *in it* just want to hear from other women who somehow made it through.  I&#39;m glad you were able to get help.  and congrats on a gorgeous baby!!  </p>
<p>It sounds like you have good support&#8211;I have a lot of books/online resources if you need more and I&#39;m happy to help.</p>
<p>Ps. we have dear friends on Bainbridge Island and the next time we visit I am putting your restaurant on the list!</p>
