      <p>I, too, suffered from postpartum depression after my first child. Unlike you, I didn&#39;t seek professional help and boy-oh-boy was that a mistake. My friend, you&#39;re going to be ok. Breath in. Breath out. Take your meds, long walks, hot baths, good naps, offered help and frequent hugs from understanding loved ones. And consider yourself hugged by this girl who&#39;s been there and the vast group of friends here whose faces you&#39;ve never seen. xoxox</p>
