      <a href="https://orangette.net/2013/01/ah-ha/#comment-39559"><time class="comment-time" datetime="2013-01-18T00:16:26-05:00">Friday, January 18, 2013 at 12:16 am</time></a>    </header>

    
    <div class="comment--content">
      <p>Thank you for sharing that photo of your beautiful little girl &#8212; mine are all grown up now, it brings back good memories.  You are a strong person, and will make it in flying colors.  It takes a lot of energy and stamina to raise children, it&#39;s a 24 hour a day job, at the start, but oh so worth it.  She will teach you in so many ways, and the person you are today will age, mellow, improve and grow into an overall better person. Get back to me in 5, 10, 20 years &#8212; even 1 year, and tell me it&#39;s not true!  It is hard.  No doubt.  But you will come through this experience wearing a true badge of honor that nothing can take away from you.  One day at a time!</p>
    </div>

