<p>My first baby is almost 21 (!), and I now realize that I had post-partum depression after she was born.  I distinctly remember that feeling of being overwhelmed and became incapacitated by the baby&#39;s needs, my emotions, my fears&#8230;  I didn&#39;t recognize what it was at the time, but maybe should have suspected since my mother went through it with my sister.  I thought it was just a reaction to my inexperience.</p>
